{"tid":331354,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"湯家驊：西九部分脫離香港領域不違基本法","createTime":"2017-07-22T06:06:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-22T06:44:36.000Z","uid":57460,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8920323fc64aaa0582a1c63f0b9dbeda444d473f","tid":331354,"uid":57460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T06:06:44.000Z","msg":"湯家驊：西九部分脫離香港領域不違基本法<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】政府最快下周公布高鐵一地兩檢方案，消息指西九龍高鐵總站將設立內地口岸區，行政會議成員湯家驊表示，如人大常委會作出決定宣布將西九部分地方脫離香港的領域，該地區就不受基本法的管轄亦不存在違反基本法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=229352&amp;refer=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D229352%26refer%3Dshare&d=2Yu%2B9NqC7gQ3dQGc9WbouP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=88bf688b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D229352%26refer%3Dshare&h=a1dda0e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=229352&amp;refer=share</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">西九獨立？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"49a78eefae929c065e36651910862765a36767d7","tid":331354,"uid":57460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T06:07:27.000Z","msg":"屌唔記得轉時事台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96b32fd999fb8b66eede53f39363b51b2a623fa6","tid":331354,"uid":125773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T06:11:31.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人大常委話成個香港都脫離香港都得啦弱智<br />\n同共產黨講法治真係曬鳩氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b18a5cf69b1693c69e8b4be4b8f450e88a8005f","tid":331354,"uid":57460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T06:41:08.000Z","msg":"最諷刺係竟然由一個話堅守法治嘅人講出口。"},{"pid":"46ed7fe9b583cac0ab6a19abe8d9ab302bbfb3a2","tid":33